products.title: Indonesia Tropical Curtain
products.description: Decorated with pretty blooms in cheerful tropical tones of green and blue, the indonesia tropical curtain is an uplifting accessory for styling your windows. The pencil pleat header gives an appealing flow to this charming cotton curtain, and it is fully lined in a luxury poly cotton mix.
